item.content:encoded:
Webbi Boi 3D is a Spiderman simulation game. You are a special agent who can launch webs to strike bad guys and move on different terrains. Your mission is to eliminate all bad guys by launching the web and catching them, then you can strike them down with your fists automatically.
On PC and MobileHold and swipe the screen = aim
